{"id": 2448, "genre": 1001, "title": "一个人住有哪些让你欲罢不能的好处？", "description": "一个人住久了，再也不习惯和另一个人一起的那些小习惯。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Diane Labombarbe）", "record_count": 7978, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201807031153465SR8hEXMgj6qbCVl.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-26T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 294656, "content": "多到高潮", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 403368}, {"id": 294912, "content": "对不起?只有两个人住一起久了改不掉的习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415469}, {"id": 294657, "content": "想怎么放飞自我就怎么放飞自我，哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400771}, {"id": 294913, "content": "无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415480}, {"id": 295169, "content": "全是好处", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416508}, {"id": 299009, "content": "可以想什么时候睡就什么时候睡，怎么折腾都不怕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202004}, {"id": 294658, "content": "省钱 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404703}, {"id": 294914, "content": "全是好处", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252902}, {"id": 302850, "content": "自由 无拘无束", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465800}, {"id": 294659, "content": "当然是想干嘛干嘛啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390650}, {"id": 295171, "content": "总结家里没人   自己可以为所欲为", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382657}, {"id": 294660, "content": "没人念", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176028}, {"id": 294916, "content": "野人一枚", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406039}, {"id": 296452, "content": "自由，不受他人约束", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421471}, {"id": 298244, "content": "放声歌唱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108770}, {"id": 294661, "content": "可以完全放松身体，掏空思想，躺在床上裸睡，无所顾忌！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1413933}, {"id": 294917, "content": "想干什么就干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403791}, {"id": 296709, "content": "身心的放松，可以做真实的自己，想怎么样怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425619}, {"id": 294662, "content": "想吃什么就叫什么，也不用注意形象...", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414674}, {"id": 294918, "content": "祼睡，慎独！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415022}, {"id": 298246, "content": "一个人瞎几把睡一张床", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108770}, {"id": 294663, "content": "放肆哭，多大声也没关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869386}, {"id": 294919, "content": "人多了会不自在呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415492}, {"id": 295431, "content": "可以直到把自己都臭得不行了，才洗头。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417486}, {"id": 294664, "content": "可以按照自己的想法布置 裸睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208695}, {"id": 294920, "content": "享受一下王维《竹里馆》的意境?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415495}, {"id": 295944, "content": "领地不被侵占感，家里的摆设是自己的风格。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1421488}, {"id": 294665, "content": "两个字 自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1414415}, {"id": 294666, "content": "哈哈哈，正打算搬出来一个人住", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838588}, {"id": 294922, "content": "哈哈哈，放飞自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581744}, {"id": 294667, "content": "唱那些跑调的歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834184}, {"id": 294923, "content": "一个人住最大的好处是可以不用开口说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415504}, {"id": 294924, "content": "想睡到什么时候起床都可以！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327163}, {"id": 295180, "content": "不用附和别人的选择，想坐哪坐那，自己想干嘛干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416499}, {"id": 294669, "content": "可以不必在乎别人的眼光", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404729}, {"id": 294925, "content": "放屁", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 442665}, {"id": 295437, "content": "撸管。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417839}, {"id": 294926, "content": "想吃什么做什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415509}, {"id": 295182, "content": "屋子能有多乱就多乱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416529}, {"id": 294671, "content": "学习可以进入freestyle啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1387958}, {"id": 294927, "content": "可以不收拾窝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1415511}, {"id": 295439, "content": "可以不穿衣服去洗澡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396693}, {"id": 294672, "content": "干一些适合一个人干的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951391}, {"id": 294928, "content": "想去哪就去哪，想吃什么就吃什么，想几点睡就几点睡。不用在意任何人的心情，也不用管任何人的感受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406690}, {"id": 295696, "content": "可以自在葛优瘫，不用注意形象。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116698}, {"id": 295952, "content": "任何时候都可以全裸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 